      "span_text": "Of note, little dose-response has been observed in other ERA studies in PAH-the BREATHE-1 study (10) showed a nonstatistically significant trend toward a larger increase in 6MWD with the higher dose of bosentan, whereas no dose-response was observed for 6MWD in the sitaxsentan STRIDE-1 study [CITATION_1] ."
